  "remarks": "RFNC – All-Russia Research Institute of Technical Physics named after Academician E.I. Zababakhin (FSUE RFNC-VNIITF) conducts research in the field of weapons and military equipment. Its main activities include development of explosive materials for military and industrial purposes and development of non-nuclear warheads and ammunition for non-nuclear weapons and military equipment. The Micro Data Center of FSUE RFNCVNIITF solves computational problems in the military and designs high-tech defence products.",
